* Waisman Laboratory for Brain Imaging and Behavior: http://brainimaging.waisman.wisc.edu/


* Carstensen Life-Span Development Lab (Stanford): www-psych.stanford.edu/~lifespan

Research focused on the social, emotional, and cognitive processes that people use to adapt to life circumstances as they age.


* Mindful Awareness Research Center (UCLA): www.marc.ucla.edu

A research center whose focus is the study of mindful awareness, especially for the
prevention and treatment of ADHD (attention deficit/hyperactivity disorder) and related
syndromes.
